Ex_3:
    Interacting with the mysql database

mysql queries:
--------------
1. show databases

>show databases;


2.create schema(DataBase)

>create schema demo;


3. switch to schema

>use demo;


4. create the table

>create table products(id integer,name varchar(20),cost integer);


5. insert the data

>insert into products values(111,'p_one',10000);


6. query the table

> select * from products;




    ************************

DataBase : demo

table    : products

    **************************